The primary target of this module is to act as a server for
JKstat

To build and run a server:

npm install express
cd node_modules
git clone https://github.com/ptribble/node-kstat
mv node-kstat kstat
cd kstat
npm build .
cd ../..
node node_modules/kstat/examples/jkstat.js

IMPORTANT: The current version is supported on Node v0.12 through Node v10.
Newer and older versions of Node won't work.
